 With the monster hit The Fusion (together with Omnia) Ukrainian dj IRA has made a massive impression on the Trance community.
 Following up the success of the original A&R release of Constant Invasions IRA has had the trancefamily excited about her remix contest.
 Sarah Russells vulnerable vocals adorn this great release!
 And next to releasing a huge BeatPort top 10 with Daniel Kandi Change The World, Sarah has been generating support by all the big DJs (Armin van Buuren, Ferry Corsten, Beat Service, Markus Schulz and many more). Dream State (with Two&One) was handpicked by Armin van Buuren and featured on his leading compilation "A State Of Trance 2013"! Included are remixes by Purelight, Frainbreeze, Mike Squillo, Alexander BobkoV and Orbion. Further on the Chill Out front we have Zetandel giving his unique laid-back sound.
 Enjoy!
